* explain why decentralized is inherently good, e.g.:
 * resiliency
 * crisis preparedness and response
 * we have to expect people and orgs to act in their own self-interest
  * it’s not healthy for them or us if we don’t
 * centralized services are be definition acting primarily in the self-interest of the owner
